name: SUNSET SARSAPARILLA
description:
"The most popular Beverage in the West!"

Sunset Sarsaparilla is a sweet carbonated sarsaparilla-based beverage that is found around the Mojave Wasteland. Look for the rare blue star on the back of your bottlecap!

Side effects include:  kidney damage, nausea, digital numbness, anxiety, loss of visual acuity, dizziness, occasional nosebleeds, joint inflammation, tooth decay, sore throat, bronchitis, organ rupture, and halitosis.
